description: 100% Pure  Protects Chapped Skin   Condition: Skin in need of protection from wind burn and environmental factors. Derived from the wool of sheep, lanolin is remarkably close to our own natural skin oils and has a texture that is similar to petroleum jelly. It is perfect for use on very dry, rough or chapped skin.
